04:11.677 --> 04:13.644
- Mm.
- Come on.

04:23.789 --> 04:25.756
- Oh, God.
- It's okay. Go ahead.

04:32.864 --> 04:34.765
And she likes it.

04:34.800 --> 04:37.468
What? I'm an open-minded woman.

04:37.502 --> 04:38.803
