in the middle of it?

05:05.664 --> 05:07.565
<i>Things came to</i>
<i>an early resolution.</i>

05:07.599 --> 05:08.733
You got fired.

05:08.767 --> 05:10.568
No. Why do you assume that?

05:10.602 --> 05:12.470
Years of experience.

05:12.504 --> 05:15.740
