that it's my fault.

05:22.681 --> 05:24.415
So you quit.

05:24.449 --> 05:25.716
I didn't want to swallow
the entire cost.

05:25.751 --> 05:28.386
Or have them recommend you
to their friends for more work.

05:28.420 --> 05:29.553
You know, I don’t wanna fight.

05:29.588 --> 05:32.390
I just want to know if
you're coming to the trial.

05:32.424 --> 05:35.393
You know my situation.
Unless I'm called to testify,

05:35.427 --> 05:36.794
I have no place in it.

05:36.828 --> 05:39.830
I was hoping you could
come for me.

05:41.800 --> 05:43.401
I'm sorry.

05:58.683 --> 05:59.817
Oh. Hey, guys.

05:59.851 --> 06:01.385
Nikki, this is Emmett.

06:01.420 --> 06:02.820
The drummer I was
telling you about.

06:02.854 --> 06:05.389
Oh, cool. I'm Nikki.

06:05.424 --> 06:06.557
Nikki.

06:09.795 --> 06:11.495
He wants to check out
the drums.

06:11.530 --> 06:13.664
Oh, yeah. Totally. Be my guest.

06:22.874 --> 06:25.476
I know this is going
to sound terrible,

06:25.510 --> 06:27.845
but I honestly thought you
were kidding when you said

06:27.879 --> 06:29.413
you had a deaf drummer.

06:29.448 --> 06:31.415
